OpenAIRE INSTALLATION
=====================

About
=====

This document specifies how to build, customize, and install the OpenAIRE
overlay onto of Invenio. Basically you install Invenio as usual and afterwards
you install OpenAIRE.

After installing be sure to run:

	inveniocfg --update-all
	inveniocfg --create-tables 

Before installing the OpenAIRE overlay create a file config-local.mk in the
root of OpenAIRE (see config.mk for further details). Afterwards, install 
the overlay:

	make 
	make install
	
	inveniocfg --update-all
	inveniocfg --reset-all